| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6596 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4347e9db-2b53-5cf5-9ad1-66bfd3643227"
